<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IFRS03_64G"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>64G</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 3"/><data name="paranum" value="64G"/></prolog><body><variant base="F21340536" id="IFRS03_64G_V1"> <p id="IFRS03_P0266"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> (Amendments to <xref base="F24730841" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_TOC.dita#IFRS10_TOC0001" id="IFRS03_X0342">IFRS 10</xref>, <xref base="F24730842" href="../ifrs12/IFRS12_TOC.dita#IFRS12_TOC0001" id="IFRS03_X0343">IFRS 12</xref> and <xref base="F24730843" href="../ias27/IAS27_TOC0001.dita#IAS27_TOC0001" id="IFRS03_X0344">IAS 27</xref>), issued in October 2012, amended <xref base="F24730844" href="IFRS03_7.dita#IFRS03_7/IFRS03_7_V2" id="IFRS03_X0345">paragraph 7</xref> and added <xref base="F24730845" href="IFRS03_2A.dita#IFRS03_2A/IFRS03_2A_V1" id="IFRS03_X0346">paragraph 2A</xref>. An entity shall apply those amendments for annual periods beginning on or after 1 January 2014. Earlier application of <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> is permitted. If an entity applies these amendments earlier it shall also apply all amendments included in <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> at the same time.</p></variant></body></paragraph>